description:
Improve your secure coding skills by joining the UK Wide OWASP Secure Coding Tournament!

The closing ceremony where we announce the winners, is on: Tuesday 3rd Nov 6pm ( UK time) - streamed via YouTube OWASP WIA at: https://youtu.be/2-9zIoen0r8

Remember :
- You can still register for the tournament at:
https://discover.securecodewarrior.com/OWASPUKBristol.html
- It takes about 1-2 hours to do the challenges
- You can see the instructions at: https://youtu.be/Jfzm3Gt1GLU?t=494

Participants can either dial in via Zoom or join the stream via YouTube at: https://youtu.be/2-9zIoen0r8
